description: Another "former customer" told his friend in need about me. I know I should keep a low profile but I must admit, I´m flattered and I welcome new opportunities to have fun. Anyways, the guy who called me crashed a car into a street lamp. He run away and went to the police a few days later. Too bad for him, the car wasn´t his, he borrowed it. He needed 20 000 for the repair otherwise the owner would kick his butt and tell the police the whole story. My lending terms were too harsh for him so I offered him the "alternative." He wasn´t happy about it but agreed eventually. I didn´t have sex since the last guy so I was super horny. The poor boy had the whole face covered in cum...
title: Debt Dandy 165
